知名外企,七险一金,双休不打卡,弹性工作制
职位描述：
Overview: 
This role will be working closely with the Hardware & Software development team to ensure the overall quality of conference related hardware products.
Responsibilities: 
·         Establish qualification and Reliability test strategy; 
·         Take the responsibility of reliability test (environmental test and Halt test)
·         Perform board-level hardware QA testing, including SI, PI, THERMAL, and EMC etc. 
·         Assistant EE engineer, implementing schematics review, PCB review. 
Qualifications: 
·         Electronic Engineering or equivalent specialty 
·         2+ years electronics design experience, and 2+ years electronics test experience 
·         Strong knowledge on hardware product test method and test equipment, rich experience using test equipment, such as high-speed oscilloscope, thermal chamber, HALT chamber, etc. 
·         Familiar with common components and interfaces, like Power regulator(DC/DC &LDO), memory(DDR, Flash，EMMC),USB interface and HDMI and Ethernet interface, etc.
          Familiar with the automated testing will be given priority
·         Experience of failure data analysis and technical test report writing 
·         Excellent written and oral communication skills (Mandarin and English)
